title: Tasia Had a Baby & Camo's in Los Angeles: Catching You Up on Everything
description:
While you're eating turkey, catch yourself on all the tea that's happened recently in Tasia and Camo's life. This is the episode right before Tasia gave birth to a beautiful baby boy and Camo was getting ready for their big trip to Los Angeles, possibly their new home. Tasia explains some recent TikTok and social media posts that have stirred up some controversy and compares this pregnancy to her pregnancy with Greenly. Camo talks about their upcoming trip as well as leaving behind some fair-weather friends.u Plus, an update on Tasia's tattoo journey from a few episodes ago.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
